Valued Advisers Trust - BFS Equity Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 11:12 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Valued Advisers Trust - BFS Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Valued Advisers Trust - BFS Equity Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by Valued Advisers Trust. The fund is managed by Bradley Foster & Sargent, Inc. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth oriented and event driven stocks of large-cap companies having market capitalizations of $10 billion or more. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors like strong management, a proven business model, a wide moat to protect against competitive threats, leading brands, excellent market positions, returns on equit...
Valued Advisers Trust - BFS Equity Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched by Valued Advisers Trust. The fund is managed by Bradley Foster & Sargent, Inc. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth oriented and event driven stocks of large-cap companies having market capitalizations of $10 billion or more. The fund employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis by focusing on factors like strong management, a proven business model, a wide moat to protect against competitive threats, leading brands, excellent market positions, returns on equity, consistent growth of earnings and revenues, above average margins, balance sheet strength, and effective allocation of cash flow to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. Valued Advisers Trust - BFS Equity Fund was formed on September 23, 2013 and is domiciled in the United States.
